OL,3,CReports of vehicle in river as Wales
OL,4,Cset to face more severe weather
OL,6,FEmergency services have confirmed
OL,7,Freports of a vehicle in the River Taff
OL,8,Fas Wales is set to face more severe
OL,9,Fweather this weekend.
OL,11,FA white van was allegedly spotted
OL,12,Ffloating in the river near the Berw
OL,13,FRoad Bridge (White Bridge) in
OL,14,FPontypridd.
OL,16,FLocals became alarmed when they
OL,17,Fspotted the object in the water, with
OL,18,Fimages posted in a community Facebook
OL,19,Fgroup showing emergency services
OL,20,Fattending the scene.
