OL,3,CReports of vehicle in river as Wales
OL,4,Cset to face more severe weather
OL,6,FIn a statement, South Wales Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service said: "SWFRS received a
OL,8,Fcall at approximately 15:29 to reports
OL,9,Fof a vehicle in a river in Pontypridd.
OL,11,F"Crews, appliances and rescue tenders
OL,12,Ffrom Ebbw Vale and Pontypridd are
OL,13,Fcurrently on scene. The incident is on-
OL,14,Fgoing."
OL,16,FSouth Wales Police also confirmed that
OL,17,Fthey were called just after 3.15pm due
OL,18,Fto reports of a van being in the river.
