OL,6,FThey said: "White Bridge is closed.
OL,7,FThe incident is ongoing, and officers
OL,8,Fare in attendance assisting with
OL,9,Ftraffic management in order that
OL,10,Femergency service colleagues can
OL,11,Feffectively deal with the incident."
OL,13,FNatural Resources Wales has just
OL,14,Fissued a flood alert for the River
OL,15,FTaff.
