OL,3,CReports of vehicle in river as Wales
OL,4,Cset to face more severe weather
OL,6,FIt says: "Flooding of low-lying land
OL,7,Fand roads is expected. Rainfall is
OL,8,Fcurrently affecting this area. River
OL,9,FLevels are above normal levels.
OL,10,FFurther heavy rain is forecast over
OL,11,Fthe weekend from Storm Darragh. We
OL,12,Fwill continue to monitor the
OL,13,Fsituation."
OL,15,FThe Met Office has warned of the
OL,16,Farrival of Storm Darragh this weekend,
OL,17,Fissuing three yellow warnings and an
OL,18,Famber weather warning for wind.
