OL,3,CReports of vehicle in river as Wales
OL,4,Cset to face more severe weather
OL,6,FWinds are expected to reach around
OL,7,F70mph, with people being advised of a
OL,8,F"danger to life" from flying debris as
OL,9,Fwell as from large waves at the coast.
OL,11,FThere could also be possible delays to
OL,12,Froad, rail and ferry travel during the
OL,13,Fpoor weather.
OL,15,FTorrential rain and flooding is
OL,16,Fexpected throughout the weekend.
OL,18,FIt follows Storm Bert which caused
OL,19,Fsevere flooding across Wales last
OL,20,Fweek, with Pontypridd being one of the
OL,21,Fworst hit areas.
